### Abby W
I ADORE this app, it makes keeping track of my income and expenses so much more manageable and has helped me save a ton now that I know where my money is going, all WITHOUT requiring my bank account information. I love how customizable it is, and the statistics are a very nice plus! The ads are not intrusive of the app in any way, shape, or form, but regardless the lifetime subscription is only $5.49. The developers have done such a phenomenal job on this app, I recommend it to everyone!

