### Trippin Dippy
Two months in and this app has been great! The only complaint is that there's no way to see a current available balance if you've put in information for future payments/bills which is inconvenient for people that have auto pay bills and are salaried so paychecks remain the same. If that feature is ever added itd be an easy 5 stars.

